Markii la [[Furashada makka|furtay makka]] sanadkii 8aad hijiriga wuxuu Nabiga scw u xushay [[cataab bin useyd]] inuu tujiyo salaada, mucaadna wuxuuna faray inuu dadka baro [[Qur'aan|Qur'aanka]] oo u sharaxo mabaadi'da diinta, Markii uu waajibkaas gutay oo uu [[Medina|Madiina]] ku soo laabtay, waxa uu sii waday baridda [[Qur'aan|qur’aanka]] iyo cilmiga diinta, wuxuu la tukan jiray nabiga scw kadib  tolkiisa ree banii salima ayuu aadi jiray oo tujin jiray<ref>https://islamic-content.com/hadeeth/929</ref> waxaa dhacday mar inuu ka soo dacwooday nin cabanaya salaada oo dadka ku dheereen jiray, nabiga scw ayaa aad uga carooday waxa uu faray inuu fududeeyo salaada maadaama uu ku daba tukanayaan qof weyn, qof yar iyo mid dan leh <ref> https://www.alukah.net/sharia/0/149351/%D8%B4%D8%B1%D8%AD-%D8%AD%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%AB-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%8A-%D9%85%D8%B3%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF-%22%D8%A5%D9%86-%D9%85%D9%86%D9%83%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%86%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%86%22/ </ref>

Sanadkii 9aad hijiriga nabiga scw ayaa u diray cariga [[yaman]] si uu dadka diinta ugu yeero, waxa uu siiyay dadrdaan oo ku dhahaayay; <blockquote> mucaadow waxaa u tagi doontaa qolo [[ahlu kitaab]] ah waxa ugu horeeya aa ugu yeereeso ha ahaado inay Alla waxidaan, hadeey kaa yeelaan ogeysii inuu Alla ku faral yeelay shan salaadood maalin kasta iyo habeen kasta, hadeey kaa yeelaan ogeysii inuu Alla ku faral yeelay sadaqo laga qaadaayo kuwooda taajiriinta ah laguna celinaayo kuwooda fuqarada ah, hadeey kaa iska jir xoolahooda wanaagsan kana dhowrso habaarka qofka dhibana ah uma dhaxeeyo asaga iyo Alla wax xijaab ah <ref> https://hadeethenc.com/ar/browse/hadith/3390 </ref></blockquote>

In mudo ah ayuu ka waday mucaad dacwad dhulka [[yaman]] wuxuuna ka xaqiijiyay guulo fara badan wuxuu soo saaray jiil door muhiim ah ka qaatay [[dagaaladii ridada]] iyo [[furashooyinka shaam]] iyo [[ciraaq]], sidoo kale masjidkii ugu horeeyay ayuu ka dhisay dhulka [[yaman]] <ref> https://www.albayan.ae/supplements/ramadan/sites/2012-08-05-1.1701969?ot=ot.AMPPageLayout </ref>, intuu ku maqnaa yaman ayuu dhintay rasuulka scw.

=== Waqtigii khulafa raashidiin ===
khilaafada [[Abu Bakr|abuubakar]] ayuu ka soo laabtay [[Yemen|yaman]] wuxuu ku sugnaa [[Medina|madiina]] ilaa waagii [[Cumar (saxaaba)|cumar]] markaas oo dalbadeen ree [[shaam]] dad [[Qur'aan|quraanka]] bara iyo axkaamta sharciga, cumar ayaa isugu yeeray shan [[Ansaar|ansaarta]] ka mid ah oo xafideen [[Qur'aan|quraanka]] Xilligii rasuulka scw, kuwaas oo kala ahaa; mucaad, [[ubay bin kacab]], [[abuu dardaa]], [[Abuu ayuub al-ansaari|abuu ayuub]] iyo [[cabaada bin saamit]], wuxuu u sheegay inay iska sooraan rag aado [[shaam]], waxey dhaheen [[Abuu ayuub al-ansaari|abuu ayuub]] waa odey da' ah [[Ubay bin kacab|Ubayna]] wuu xanuunsan yahay, sedexda soo hartay ayaa baxeeso, [[Cumar (saxaaba)|cumar]] wuxuu u kala diray [[ximsa]], [[dimishiq]] iyo [[falastiin]], mucaad wuxuu u baxay [[ximsa]], halkaas ayuu ka bilaabay faafinta diinta.

Mid ka mid ah [[taabiciinta]] oo sheekeenaya ayaa yiri; waxaa soo galay masjidka xamza waxaa uu ku arkay wiil dhalinyaro ah oo dadka ku hareersan yihiin iskuna cariirinaayaan, aad moodid inuu afkiisa kasoo baxaayo nuur iyo [[Luul (macdan)|luul]], waxaa  dhahay yaa waay kan? Waxee dhaheen waa mucaad <ref>https://www.islam.ms/ar/%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B0-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AC%D8%A8%D9%84</ref>.

=== Dhimashadiis ===
waxaa ka dilaacay dhulka [[shaam]] daacuun loo bixiyay [[daacuunkii camwaas]] kaas oo ay ku la'deen kumanaan muslimiinta ka mid ah, waxaa ku jiray dadka ku dhintay [[Abuu Cubeydah Caamir ibn Jaraax|abuu cubeyda]] hogaamiyihii shaam  wuxuuna ka dardaarmay inuu mucaad hogaamiyo muslimiinta<ref name="سعد5">[https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1102 الطبقات الكبرى لابن سعد - مُعَاذُ بْنُ جَبَلِ (5)] {{Wayback|url=https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1102 |date=20170415013238 }} {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415013238/http://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1102|date=15 أبريل 2017}}</ref>, mucaad wuxuu ahaa inuu doon doonaayay la kulanka Alle, khudbab ayuu jeediyay oo ku lahaa: '''«'''Cudurkaan waa naxariis, waa ducada nabigiina iyo dhimashada dadka wanaagsan hortiina, mucaadna wuxuu Alla weydiisanaa inuu ka siiyo mucaad iyo reerkiis qeybtooda'''»'''<ref>[https://www.alukah.net/sharia/0/33466/ أبو عبيدة بن الجراح رضي الله عنه - شبكة الألوكة] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827143450/http://www.alukah.net/sharia/0/33466|date=27 أغسطس 2017}}</ref>, wiilkiisa [[Cabdiraxmaan bin mucaad|cabdiraxmaan]] ayuu cudurka ku dhacay wuu dhintay, labadiisa xaas ayaa cudurka u dhintay, kadib mucaad ayuu cudurka haleelay asna wuu ku dhintay<ref name="سعد6">[https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1103 الطبقات الكبرى لابن سعد - مُعَاذُ بْنُ جَبَلِ (6)] {{Wayback|url=https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1103 |date=20170415013807 }} {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415013807/http://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1103|date=15 أبريل 2017}}</ref>, daacuunkaan wuxuu ahaa sanadii 18aad ee hijriga.

Mucaad wuxuu dhahay markuu sakaraadka u yimid:  '''«'''fiiriya waaga ma baryay?'''»''' '''«'''waxaa la dhahay may wali ma baryin'''»''' xoogaa ka dib ayaa baa lagu dhahay wuu baryay, wuxuu dhahay: '''«'''Alla ayaa ka magan galay habeen subaxdeedu naar tahay, soo dhawaaw mowdoow mid booqdo oo la jecel yahow, Allahayow waxaa ahaa inaa kaa baqaayo, maantase waa ku rajeynaa, waa ogtahay inaa aduunyada u jecleen talaalida geedaha iyo dureerinta wabiyada, laakin inaa oomo maalin weynta oo dhibtooda saacadaha iyo inaa culumada ku cariirsado xalqadaha'''»'''<ref>https://mqaall.com/the-death-of-muadh-bin-jabal/</ref>.

== Darajadiisa cilmiga ==
Mucaad wuxuu laazimay Nebiga scw tan iyo markii [[Medina|madiina]] u soo hijrooday wuxuu ka bartay [[Qur'aan|quraanka]] iyo axkaamta shareecada heer wuxuu gaaray inuu ka mid dad yar waagii rasuulka scw dadka u iftoon jireen <ref> http://m-noor.com/showthread.php?p=28641</ref> 

'''[[Anas bin maalik]]''' ayaa yiri «waqtigii rasuulka scw afar qof oo ree [[ansaar]] ah ayaa [[Qur'aan|quraanka]] dhan xifdiyeen waana [[ubay bin kacab]], [[Mucaad Bin Jabal|mucaad bin jabal]], [[zeyd bin saabit]] iyo Abuu zeyd oo ina adeertey ka mid ahaa»

Xadiis uu Nebiga scw ku xusay fadliga saxaabada qaar ayaa ahaa «Umadeyda waxaa ugu naxariis badan umada [[Abu Bakr|abuubakar]], waxaa ugu daran diinta allah [[Cumar (saxaaba)|cumar]], waxaa ugu run sheeg badan xishoodka [[Cusmaan bin Cafaan|cusmaan]] waxaa ugu aqoon badan xakaasha iyo xaaraanta [[Mucaad Bin Jabal|mucaad]], waxaa ugu dhaxl siin badan [[zeyd bin saabit]], umad kasta amiin bay leedahay amiinka umadaana waa [[Abuu Cubeydah Caamir ibn Jaraax|abuu cubeyda]]» <ref>رواه ابن حبان، في صحيح ابن حبان، عن أنس بن مالك، الصفحة أو الرقم: 7252، أخرجه في صحيحه

